<blockquote>
<p>KoÊ»rish usulini oÊ»zgartirish uchun shunchaki Saqlangan xabarlaringiz <strong>yuqori panelini</strong> bosing. Shuningdek, â‹® / â‹¯ belgisini bosib, <em>â€œXabarlar sifatida koÊ»rishâ€</em> yoki <em>â€œChatlar sifatida koÊ»rishâ€</em> bandini tanlashingiz mumkin â€” bu holatda Saqlangan xabarlar keyingi safar ochganingizda tanlangan rejimda koÊ»rsatiladi.</p>
</blockquote>
<h3><a class="anchor" name="saqlangan-xabarlar-uchun-teglar" href="#saqlangan-xabarlar-uchun-teglar"><i class="anchor-icon"></i></a><img class="icon" src="../../file/464001305/110b0/-bpC5P3HJp4.6317/a2b79589744c739331.html" alt="Premium"> Saqlangan xabarlar uchun teglar</h3>
<p>QoÊ»shimcha tartiblash uchun qidiruvda tezda <strong>filtrlash</strong> imkonini beradigan Saqlangan xabarlarga <strong>bir nechta teg</strong> kiritishingiz mumkin.</p>
<p>Teglar <strong>emojiga</strong> asoslanishi sababli teg kiritish reaksiya kiritish kabi oson, lekin teglarda <strong>nomlar</strong> ham boÊ»lishi mumkin. Teglardan allaqachon barcha Telegram Premium foydalanuvchilari foydalanishi mumkin.</p>
