<h3><a class="anchor" name="yangilangan-qidiruv" href="#yangilangan-qidiruv"><i class="anchor-icon"></i></a>Yangilangan qidiruv</h3>
<p>Biz barcha chatlarda <strong>qidiruvni</strong> yaxshiladik: endi qidiruv natijalaringiz boÊ»ylab <strong>harakatlanish</strong> va ularni <strong>ixcham roÊ»yxat</strong> sifatida koÊ»rish osonroq.</p>
