<h3><a class="anchor" name="bir-martalik-ovozli-va-video-xabarlar" href="#bir-martalik-ovozli-va-video-xabarlar"><i class="anchor-icon"></i></a>Bir martalik ovozli va video xabarlar</h3>
<p><a href="../channel-stories/uz5279.html?ln=a#bir-martalik-media">Bir martalik sozlamasidan</a> endi <strong>ovozli</strong> va <strong>video xabarlarda</strong> foydalanish mumkin. Bunday xabarlarni ularni qayta-qayta yuborishingizga undaydigan animatsiya bilan <strong>avtomatik oÊ»chirilishidan</strong> oldin faqat <strong>bir marta</strong> ijro qilish mumkin. </p>
