<h3><a class="anchor" name="yozuvni-pauzalash-va-davom-ettirish" href="#yozuvni-pauzalash-va-davom-ettirish"><i class="anchor-icon"></i></a>Yozuvni pauzalash va davom ettirish</h3>
<p>Istalgan <strong>ovozli</strong> yoki <strong>video xabarni</strong> yozayotganda endi bir nechta xabar yuborish oÊ»rniga yozuvni <strong>pauzalashingiz</strong> va keyin <strong>davom ettirishingiz</strong> mumkin.</p>
